    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="upa.00072.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Kirkwood (Glendale) New Jersey</name>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">U S America<ptr target="upa.00072_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1880-04-24"><hi rend="underline">April 24</hi>&#8212;</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>Down here on one of my visits<ptr target="upa.00072_n2"/>&#8212;Mr and Mrs S
                and all the young folks well as usual&#8212;E is still over at Laurel Mills,
                &#38; is well &#38; hearty&#8212;H runs the store here&#8212;(the store is
                doing middling well)&#8212;M and V and R and G<ptr
                    target="upa.00072_n3"/> all right &#38; growing fast&#8212;</p>

            <p>&#8212;Begins to look like spring&#8212;apple trees all in bloom, &#38; the sprouting wheat
                a rich emerald, beautiful&#8212;(but just to-day is raw and half-raining &#38;
                darkish)&#8212;the l[ecture] went off fairly, it was good fun for me, grave as the
                subject was&#8212;I sent you a short report&#8212;I am surprised about
                    B<ptr target="upa.00072_n4"/>&#8212;my health &#38; strength
                fair</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">W W</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="upa.00072.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
